('92986','32018','5','Exeptional low price!! Former 4 star country house hotel in the heart of Mallorca '),
('92987','32019','5','The property dating back to 1879 and stands on a ca 54.200m² large flat plot located in the heart of Mallorca. Palma de Mallorca and the airport is only 30 min. away. The very solidly built former winery was expanded and reformed in 1990 to 4 star country house hotel and operated until 2010. Since is the beautiful property empty and needs a new operator, again breathes life into this pretty hotel.  The hotel offers a reception in the main building, restaurant, large winter garden / restaurant, large ceremonial hall with 15m high vaulted ceiling (former wine warehouse), kitchen ect. \r\nIn the upper floors there are 5 spacious suites and staff accommodations. 21 large junior suites and an indoor pool with sauna are located in a neighboring building. On the ca 54.000m² large property you find a large car parking areas also an outdoor swimming pool with sun terraces, all-weather tennis court and a 9 hole pitch and putt golf course, which is unfortunately a little over grown. A large room for bicycles and bicycle service or massages is available. Currently, the expandability for more hotel rooms will be checked at the Building Department. A very interesting country house hotel, which could appear with little effort back to its former glory.\r\nThe sale price is lowered from 5,500.000  to 2,900.000 € to accommodate to the new owner with the resulting repair costs.\r\n'),
